channel.desc: Caroline Searcy's thoroughbred re-homing program Thoroughbreds Are Go returns! Trainer Gary Portelli judging at Sydney Royal Easter Show. Life With Horses welcomes Aged Care residents to mix with thoroughbreds & the slow ex-racehorse guarding racing's latest star Stefi Magnetica!
